#

Coconut Curry Shrimp

35 min
$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

Thai

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyquickcomfort food

Description

Succulent shrimp simmered in a creamy coconut curry sauce, served over rice for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • coconut milk: 1 can (13.5 oz)
  • curry paste (red or yellow): 2 tablespoons
  • bell pepper (sliced): 1
  • onion (sliced): 1
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (minced): 1 tablespoon
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • rice (for serving): 2 cups cooked
